      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "1659-1693",
      "markText": "不要尝试在软件架构中寻求最佳设计，而应力求寻找不那么糟糕的取舍组合。",
      "totalCount": 234,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300065695&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1659&rangeEnd=1693",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/18632780813ab8029g01593a?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1659&rangeEnd=1693"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300065695_7_2386-2402",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "2386-2402",
      "markText": "软件架构就是以后不好改的那些东西",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300065695&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2386&rangeEnd=2402",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/18632780813ab8029g01593a?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2386&rangeEnd=2402"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300065695_7_13983-14007",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "13983-14007",
      "markText": "“我们知道这样做不好，回头就改”——然后永不回头",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300065695&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=13983&rangeEnd=14007",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/18632780813ab8029g01593a?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=13983&rangeEnd=14007"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300065695_4_564-587",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "564-587",
      "markText": "在不确定的环境中，通过技术寻找共赢的解决方案。",
      "totalCount": 105,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300065695&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=564&rangeEnd=587",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/18632780813ab8029g01593a?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=564&rangeEnd=587"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300065695_10_10446-10497",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "10446-10497",
      "markText": "如果你的微服务必须按照特定顺序作为完整的集合部署，那么不如让它们回归单体吧，这样你还可以免去一些痛苦。",
      "totalCount": 98,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300065695&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=10446&rangeEnd=10497",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/18632780813ab8029g01593a?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=10446&rangeEnd=10497"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300065695_7_14841-14852",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "14841-14852",
      "markText": "为什么做比如何做更重要",
      "totalCount": 96,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300065695&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=14841&rangeEnd=14852",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/18632780813ab8029g01593a?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=14841&rangeEnd=14852"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300065695_4_446-481",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "446-481",
      "markText": "架构师首先是一个政治角色，其次才是技术角色。这是我作为架构师恪守的格言",
      "totalCount": 84,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300065695&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=446&rangeEnd=481",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/18632780813ab8029g01593a?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=446&rangeEnd=481"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300065695_7_7869-7949",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "7869-7949",
      "markText": "自动化治理的一个关键点便是架构特征的客观定义。举例来说，架构师不能说我想要一个“高性能”的网站，而必须提供一个可以被测试、监控或者其他适应度函数来测定的目标值。",
      "totalCount": 80,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300065695&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=7869&rangeEnd=7949",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/18632780813ab8029g01593a?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=7869&rangeEnd=7949"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300065695_7_971-1030",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "971-1030",
      "markText": "架构师很少遇到通用问题，他们持续地在各种新奇场景中艰难地做着抉择。对于架构师来说，问题就像雪花，没有两片雪花是相同的。",
      "totalCount": 75,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300065695&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=971&rangeEnd=1030",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/18632780813ab8029g01593a?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=971&rangeEnd=1030"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300065695_10_5074-5145",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "5074-5145",
      "markText": "如今的商业活动中，5个关键的架构特征支撑了敏捷性、上市速度，最终获得竞争优势，它们是可用性（容错性）、可伸缩性、可部署性、可测试性和可维护性。",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300065695&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=5074&rangeEnd=5145",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/18632780813ab8029g01593a?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=5074&rangeEnd=5145"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300065695_7_3501-3519",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "3501-3519",
      "markText": "数据很珍贵，它比系统本身存在得更久。",
      "totalCount": 60,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300065695&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3501&rangeEnd=3519",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/18632780813ab8029g01593a?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3501&rangeEnd=3519"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300065695_7_3712-3766",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "3712-3766",
      "markText": "架构师和DBA必须保证业务型数据能够在单体系统解构后存活，无论架构如何变更，业务人员应该能持续从数据中获益。",
      "totalCount": 60,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300065695&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3712&rangeEnd=3766",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/18632780813ab8029g01593a?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3712&rangeEnd=3766"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300065695_7_13835-13910",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "13835-13910",
      "markText": "架构师应该避免过度使用强大的适应度函数。他们不应该蜷缩在象牙塔里筹谋一个复杂到不可思议、环环相扣的适应度函数，那样只会让开发人员和团队感到沮丧和挫败。",
      "totalCount": 51,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300065695&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=13835&rangeEnd=13910",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/18632780813ab8029g01593a?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=13835&rangeEnd=13910"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300065695_14_11241-11291",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "11241-11291",
      "markText": "我们的建议是等待，直到一个模式建立或者持续可扩展性被确认，然后让该驱动因素成为判断粒度分解的主要手段",
      "totalCount": 51,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300065695&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=11241&rangeEnd=11291",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/18632780813ab8029g01593a?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=11241&rangeEnd=11291"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300065695_16_14534-14583",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "14534-14583",
      "markText": "共享服务技术非常适合于高度多语言的环境（具有多种异构语言和平台的环境），以及共享功能频繁变化的情况",
      "totalCount": 51,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300065695&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=14534&rangeEnd=14583",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/18632780813ab8029g01593a?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=14534&rangeEnd=14583"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300065695_23_1006-1080",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "1006-1080",
      "markText": "我们IT部门学会了宝贵的一课，就是把业务驱动因素作为处理问题的一种方式，从中催生出解决方案。以前，我们总是只关注问题的技术面，所以一直缺少大局观。”",
      "totalCount": 51,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300065695&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=1006&rangeEnd=1080",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/18632780813ab8029g01593a?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=1006&rangeEnd=1080"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300065695_23_11088-11177",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "11088-11177",
      "markText": "用通用和抽象的方式思考架构问题，无法让架构师走得更远。就如同架构问题往往能完美避开通用解决方案，对于架构师来说，重要的是自己掌握建模相关的领域能力，以便做出更好的利弊分析和决策。",
      "totalCount": 51,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300065695&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=11088&rangeEnd=11177",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/18632780813ab8029g01593a?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=11088&rangeEnd=11177"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300065695_10_12382-12467",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "12382-12467",
      "markText": "与可测试性以及可部署性一样，完成单一业务流程的服务间通信越多，对可伸缩性和弹性产生的负面影响越大。因此，当需要更高的可伸缩性和弹性水平时，最好尽可能减少服务间的同步通信。",
      "totalCount": 48,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300065695&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=12382&rangeEnd=12467",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/18632780813ab8029g01593a?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=12382&rangeEnd=12467"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300065695_11_9931-10010",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "9931-10010",
      "markText": "当把单体应用拆分为微服务时，先考虑迁移到基于服务的架构，作为走向微服务的第一步。但如果代码库就是一团毫无组织的大泥球，没什么组件呢？这时我们就需要战术分叉了。",
      "totalCount": 48,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300065695&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=9931&rangeEnd=10010",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/18632780813ab8029g01593a?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=9931&rangeEnd=10010"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300065695_13_8627-8721",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "8627-8721",
      "markText": "管理如何在分布式架构中使用数据库连接很重要。一种有效的方法是为每个服务分配一个连接配额，以管理跨服务的可用数据库连接的分布。连接配额指定了允许服务在其连接池中使用或提供的最大数据库连接数。",
      "totalCount": 48,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300065695&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=8627&rangeEnd=8721",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/18632780813ab8029g01593a?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=8627&rangeEnd=8721"
    }
  ],
